<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="as-much-as-sb-can-could-do">as much as sb can / could (do)</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-as-much-as-possible">1.<strong>尽某人最大努力 (as much as possible)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have done as much as I could do to help him. 
我已尽力去帮助他了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Students are encouraged to read as much as possible outside school. 
我们鼓励学生在课外尽量多阅读。</p></div></div>